---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us – Tony&Son Hair Salon Brussels" locale="en" page="about" description="Tony&Son, hair salon in Saint-Josse-ten-Noode, Brussels since 1970. Three generations of expertise near the Schuman quarter. Cuts, colouring, barber.">
  <!-- Title Bar -->
  <section class="titlebar" style="background-image: url('/images/about-hero.jpg')">
    <div class="titlebar-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Welcome Section -->
  <section class="welcome-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="welcome-grid">
        <div class="welcome-content">
          <h5 class="tagline">Hair salon since 1970</h5>
          <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--color-heading);">Tony&Son — Saint-Josse-ten-Noode, Brussels</h2>
          <p>Rue Bonneels 27, two minutes from Metro Schuman. The salon has been here since 1970 — Tony first, then his son Salvatore. We cut hair for EU officials between noon and two, families from Schaerbeek on Saturday mornings, expats looking for a hairdresser who speaks their language. Every client leaves with a cut that fits them, not one copied from a magazine.</p>
          <p>Cuts, colouring, balayage, straightening, barber, extensions — we do it all, but we don't do anything halfway. If a service isn't right for your hair, we tell you before we start.</p>
          <a href="https://widget.treatwell.be/fr/salon/tony-and-son/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">Book now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome-images">
          <img src="/images/about-1.jpg" alt="Tony&Son Salon" class="welcome-img-1" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/about-2.jpg" alt="Tony&Son Hairstyling" class="welcome-img-2" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- History Section -->
  <section class="history-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--color-heading);margin-bottom:50px;">The Story of Tony&Son</h2>
      <div class="history-content">
        <p>In <em>1970</em>, <strong>Tony Campisi</strong>, a young hairdresser from Italy, opened his salon in Saint-Josse-ten-Noode. No business plan, just skill and a desire to do things right. The neighbourhood was different back then — less international, more working-class. But the quality of the cuts did the rest.</p>
        <p>Over the years, the salon became an address passed down between neighbours. First-generation clients now bring their grandchildren. The formula hasn't changed: listen, advise honestly, deliver what was promised.</p>
        <p>Today, <strong>Salvatore Campisi</strong>, Tony's son, runs the salon. Trained at <em>Toni&Guy</em> in London, he brought back international techniques while keeping the family DNA. The neighbourhood has changed — the European institutions moved in, the clientele diversified — but the standards stayed the same.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Opening Hours CTA -->
  <section class="hours-cta-section">
    <div class="hours-cta-grid">
      <div class="hours-cta-left">
        <div class="hours-cta-content">
          <h5 class="tagline" style="color:var(--color-gold);">We are open</h5>
          <h2 class="hours-cta-title">Opening Hours</h2>
          <div class="hours-list">
            <p>Tuesday - Friday — 9:00 - 19:00</p>
            <p>Saturday — 9:00 - 18:00</p>
            <p>Sunday - Monday — Closed</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://widget.treatwell.be/fr/salon/tony-and-son/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn" style="background:#fff;color:#000;margin-top:40px;">Book your visit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hours-cta-right" style="background-image: url('/images/photo-11.jpeg')"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .titlebar {
    position: relative;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding: 160px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .titlebar-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .titlebar h1 {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-transform: capitalize;
  }

  .welcome-section { padding: 100px 0; }
  .welcome-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .welcome-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .welcome-images {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .welcome-img-1, .welcome-img-2 {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .history-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .history-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .history-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .history-content em { color: var(--color-gold); font-style: italic; }
  .history-content strong { color: var(--color-heading); }

  .hours-cta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 500px;
  }
  .hours-cta-left {
    background: var(--color-black);
    padding: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hours-cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .hours-list p {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .hours-cta-right {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .titlebar { padding: 120px 0 60px; }
    .titlebar h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .welcome-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .welcome-images { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hours-cta-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hours-cta-left { padding: 40px; }
    .hours-cta-right { min-height: 300px; }
  }
</style>
